Adadin wadanda suka mutu a tsunami a Indonesia ya kai 832
Adadin wadanda suka mutu sakamakon girgizar kasa da tsunami da ta auku a Indonesia ya haura zuwa 832, in ji hukumar bada agajin bala'i ta kasar a safiyar yau Lahadi.
An samu rahotannin da dama na mutane da suka nutse a cikin gine-gine da suka rushe sakamakon girgizar kasa mai karfin maki 7.5 da ta auku a ranar Juma'a da ta haifar da raƙuman ruwa mai tsayi har zuwa mita 20, in ji mai magana da yawun hukumar Sutopo Purwo Nugroho a wani taron manema labarai.
A yau, birnin Palu da ke da mazauna fiye da 380,000, ya cika da kango.
'Yan sanda sun kama wani mutum mai shekara 32 bayan da aka kashe wata mata ta hanyar bindiga.
An fara binciken kisan kai bayan da aka gano gawar wata mata a Birkenhead a yankin Merseyside da safiyar yau.
