A wata hira da aka yi da ita a kan shafinta na farko, tsohon ministan harkokin wajenta Boris Johnson ya ci gaba da kai hari kan abin da ake kira shirin Chequers na Brexit, yana mai cewa shawarar da Burtaniya da EU ke yi na karbar haraji daga juna "abin ba'a ne kwarai".
'Yan sanda sun kama Dyson Simpson wanda ake zargi da kashe dan wasan LSU
'Yan sanda sun kama wani da ake zargi da hannu a harin da ya kashe Wayde Sims, dan wasan 'yan wasan kwando na LSU mai shekara 20.
An kama Dython Simpson, mai shekara 20, aka kuma daure shi a kurkuku a kan laifin kisan kai na biyu, in ji 'yan sanda a Baton Rouge.
Jami'ai sun saki bidiyon rigima tsakanin Sims da Simpson kuma 'yan sanda sun ce Simpson ya rasa tabarau a lokacin.
'Yan sanda sun kwato tabarau daga wurin da aka kashe dan Adam, inda suka ce sun sami DNA na Simpson a kansu, kamar yadda jaridar WAFB ta CBS ta ruwaito.
Bayan sun yi wa Simpson tambayoyi, 'yan sanda sun ce ya yi ikirarin kashe Wayde.
An ba da belin sa na $350,000, a cewar lauyan sa.
Ofishin 'yan sanda na yankin Baton Rouge da ke gabashin garin ya bayar da rahoton farko a ranar Juma'a, yana mai cewa sanadin mutuwar ya kasance harbin bindiga ne a wuyansa da kuma kai.
A cewar sashen, an ba da wannan lambar yabo ne ga rundunar 'yan sanda ta Louisiana da 'yan sandan jihar da 'yan sandan jami'ar Southern da kuma mutanen da suka taimaka wajen binciken da ya kai ga kama ta.
Daraktan 'yan wasa na LSU Joe Alleva ya gode wa hukumar da ke sa ido kan doka da kuma neman adalci.
Sims yana ɗan shekara 20.
Dan wasan mai tsawon kafa 6 da inci 6 ya taso ne a Baton Rouge, inda mahaifinsa Wayne kuma ya yi wasan kwando a LSU.
A bara, ya ci kwallaye 5.6 kuma ya ci gaba da yin 2.6.
A safiyar yau ta juma'a, kocin 'yan wasan LSU, Will Wade, ya ce 'yan wasan sun yi bakin ciki kuma sun yi mamaki da mutuwar Wayde.
"Wannan shi ne abin da muke damuwa akai-akai", in ji Wade.
Dutsen mai aman wuta ya zubar da toka a kan Mexico City
Gishirin da ke zubewa daga dutsen Popocatepetl ya kai kudancin birnin Mexico.
A ranar Lahadi, cibiyar kare bala'i ta gargaɗi jama'ar Mexico su zauna a wuri mai nisa bayan da aka samu tashin hankali a cikin dutsen da kuma saurin da ake samu a cikinsa, inda aka samu iskar gas da toka guda 183 a cikin sa'o'i 24.
Cibiyar ta lura da girgizar ƙasa da kuma amo.
Hotunan da aka wallafa a shafukan sada zumunta sun nuna wani kazar turɓaya da ke rufe manyan motoci a unguwannin Mexico City kamar Xochimilco.
Masana ilimin ƙasa sun lura da ƙarin ayyukan dutsen mai fitad da wuta mai nisan mil 45 (kilomita 72) kudu maso gabashin babban birnin tun lokacin da girgizar kasa mai ƙarfin 7.1 ta girgiza tsakiyar Mexico a watan Satumbar 2017.
Dutsen da ake kira Don Goyo ya fara aiki ne a shekara ta 1994.
'Yan sanda sun yi arangama da masu neman 'yancin kai a Catalonia a ranar tunawa da zaben raba gardama
An kama mutane shida a birnin Barcelona a ranar Lahadi bayan da masu zanga-zanga masu goyon bayan 'yanci suka yi karo da 'yan sanda a lokacin da dubban mutane suka shiga zanga-zangar adawa da ranar tunawa da raba gardama da aka yi a Catalonia.
Wasu 'yan tawaye masu sanye da kayan rufe fuska, da rundunar 'yan sanda ta musamman ta tsare, sun yi ta harba su da kwai da kuma fenti masu launin toka, suna yin girgije mai duhu a kan titunan da ke cike da masu yawon bude ido.
Daga baya a ranar, an yi ta yin mu'amala da 'yan sanda, wadanda suka yi amfani da sanduna don dakile harin.
Masu goyon bayan 'yanci sun shafe sa'o'i suna rera "Babu mantuwa, babu gafara" kuma sun yi karo da masu goyon bayan Tarayyar da suke cewa "Long live Spain".
Mutane 14 sun samu jinya sakamakon karamin rauni da suka samu a zanga-zangar, in ji manema labarai na yankin.
Tashin hankali na ci gaba da hauhawa a yankin da ya yi murabus da neman 'yancin kai shekara guda bayan kada kuri'ar raba gardama a ranar 1 ga watan Oktoba, wadda Madrid ta ayyana haramtacciyar amma 'yan Catalonia masu neman' yanci sun yi farin ciki.
Masu jefa kuri'a sun zabi 'yancin kai da rinjaye, duk da cewa yawan masu jefa kuri'a ya yi kadan saboda masu adawa da rabuwa sun yi kaurin suna wajen kada kuri'ar.
A cewar hukumomin Catalonia, kusan mutane 1,000 ne suka jikkata a bara bayan da 'yan sanda suka yi kokarin dakatar da zaben ta hanyar tashin hankali a wuraren zabe a fadin yankin.
Kungiyoyin masu goyon bayan 'yancin kai sun yi zango a daren Juma'a don hana zanga-zanga da kuma tallafawa 'yan sanda na kasa.
An yi zanga-zangar, amma an canza hanya.
Wani mai aikin lantarki mai suna Narcis Termes, mai shekara 68 wanda ya shiga zanga-zangar neman 'yanci tare da matarsa, ya ce ba ya jin dadin samun 'yancin kai na Catalonia.
Shekarar da ta shige ta kasance ɗaya daga cikin lokutan farin ciki a rayuwarmu.
Na ga iyayena suna kuka saboda farin ciki saboda an basu damar yin zabe, amma yanzu muna cikin matsala, "in ji shi.
Duk da samun nasara a zaben kananan hukumomi a watan Disambar da ya gabata, jam'iyyun Catalonia masu neman 'yancin kai sun sha wahala wajen samun karfin guiwa, saboda wasu daga cikin sanannun shugabanninsu na gudun hijira ko kuma tsare, suna jiran a yi masu shari'a kan rawar da suka taka a zaben raba gardama, sannan a ayyana 'yancin kai.
Joan Puig, mai aikin mota mai shekara 42 wanda ya dauki hoton wani zanga-zanga na goyon bayan 'yan sanda, ya ce 'yan siyasa a bangarorin biyu sun goyi bayan rikicin.
"Ya zama mafi wuya", in ji shi.
A ranar Asabar, Oriol Junqueras, daya daga cikin shugabannin Catalonia tara da aka tsare tun karshen shekarar da ta gabata, ya sanar da cewa zai tsaya takarar neman zaben 'yan majalisar Turai a shekara mai zuwa.
"Tasarin shiga zaben na Turai shi ne hanya mafi kyau da za a yi tir da koma bayan dabi'un dimokiradiyya da kuma matsin da gwamnatin Spain ta yi mana", in ji shi.
