Taron Trump a Yammacin Virginia, tashar YouTube
Shugaba Donald Trump ya fara jerin tarurrukan neman zabe a wannan dare a Wheeling, West Virginia.
Wannan shi ne na farko cikin taron da Trump zai yi a mako mai zuwa, wanda ya hada da ziyarar da zai yi a wurare masu kyau kamar Tennessee da Mississippi.
Yayin da ake jiran a yi masa kuri'a don cike gurbin da ke a kotun koli, Trump na shirin kara goyon baya a zaben da za a yi a tsakiyar shekara mai zuwa saboda 'yan Republican na hadarin rasa ikon majalisar dattawa bayan zaben na watan Nuwamba.
Yaushe ne taron Trump a West Virginia a yau da kuma yadda za ku iya kallon shi a kan layi?
An shirya taron Trump a Wheeling, West Virginia da karfe bakwai na yammacin yammacin yammacin yau Asabar, 29 ga Satumba, 2018.
Za ku iya kallon taron Trump a West Virginia a nan a wani bidiyo da aka saka kai tsaye a YouTube.
Trump zai yi magana a kan batun da aka gabatar a wannan makon game da nadin Brett Kavanaugh a matsayin babban alkali wanda ya fuskanci tashin hankali sakamakon zargin da ake yi masa na cin zarafin mata, kuma ana sa ran za a dage zaman majalisa na tsawon kwanaki bakwai, yayin da FBI ke ci gaba da gudanar da bincike.
Amma babban burin wannan taron shi ne ya taimaka wa 'yan Republican su samu nasara a zaben Nuwamba.
A saboda haka ne, masu fafutukar neman zaben shugaban kasa Trump suka ce an gudanar da taron ne a wannan makon domin karfafawa 'yan sa kai da magoya baya karfi, yayin da 'yan Republican ke kokarin karewa da kuma kara yawan kujerun da suke da su a majalisar dattijai da majalisar wakilai, kamar yadda kamfanin dillancin labarai na Reuters ya ruwaito.
"Samun iko da majalisa wani muhimmin bangare ne na ajandar shugaban kasa, don haka zai yi tafiya zuwa kasashe da dama yayin da muke shiga kakar yakin neman zabe", in ji wani mai magana da yawun Trump, wanda ya ki bayyana sunansa.
An shirya taron ne a filin wasa na Westbank Arena da ke Wheeling, kuma taron na daren yau zai iya jawo hankalin 'yan kallo daga Ohio da Pennsylvania, da kuma hankalin 'yan jarida daga Pittsburgh, a cewar wata rahoto da West Virginia Metro News ta fitar.
A ranar Asabar, za a yi ziyarar Trump ta biyu a wannan watan zuwa West Virginia, jihar da ya lashe zaben da kashi 40 cikin dari a 2016.
Trump na kokarin taimaka wa Patrick Morrissey, dan takarar Republican a majalisar dattijai daga West Virginia, wanda ba ya yin fice a zaben fidda gwani.
"Ba alama ce mai kyau ba ga Morrissey cewa shugaban kasa ya zo don kokarin tayar da shi a cikin binciken", in ji Simon Haeder, masanin siyasa a Jami'ar West Virginia, a cewar rahoton Reuters.
