HIV/AIDS: China ta ba da rahoton karuwar sabbin masu cutar 14%
Kasar Sin ta samu karuwar mutane 14 cikin 100 da suka kamu da cutar HIV da AIDS.
Fiye da mutane 820,000 a ƙasar sun kamu da cutar, in ji jami'an kiwon lafiya.
Kimanin sabbin maganganu 40,000 aka rubuta a cikin kwata na biyu na 2018 kawai.
Yawancin sababbin cututtuka ana samunsu ne ta hanyar jima'i, wanda ya bambanta da yadda ake samun su a dā.
A dā, cutar HIV ta yadu a wasu wurare a ƙasar Sin ta wurin ƙarin jini da aka yi wa wanda yake da cutar.
Amma, adadin mutanen da suke kamuwa da cutar HIV ta wannan hanyar ya ragu zuwa kusan babu, in ji ma'aikatan kiwon lafiya na kasar Sin a wani taro da aka yi a lardin Yunnan.
Amma, a shekara guda, adadin mutanen da suke da kwayar cutar HIV da AIDS a China ya ƙaru da mutane 100,000.
Cutar HIV ta hanyar jima'i babbar matsala ce a tsakanin 'yan luwadi na kasar Sin.
