Berners-Lee ya canza Intanet a 1994 lokacin da ya kafa kungiyar yanar gizo ta duniya a Massachusetts Institute of Technology.
A cikin 'yan watannin nan, Berners-Lee ya zama sanannen murya a cikin tattaunawar tsaka tsaki na yanar gizo.
Duk da cewa zai fara Inrupt, Berners-Lee zai kasance mai kafa da kuma darektan kungiyar World Wide Web Consortium, da Gidauniyar Gidan yanar gizo da kuma Cibiyar Bayanai ta Bude.
"Ina da kwarin gwiwa game da wannan sabon zamanin na yanar gizo", in ji Berners-Lee.
