Taron Trump da Rosenstein na iya sake jinkirta, in ji fadar White House
Babban taron Donald Trump da mataimakin babban lauya Rod Rosenstein na iya jinkirta zuwa mako guda saboda ci gaba da fafatawa da dan takarar da zai zama alkalin kotun kolin Amurka, Brett Kavanaugh, a cewar fadar White House a ranar Lahadi.
Rosenstein ya jagoranci aikin mai ba da shawara na musamman Robert Mueller, wanda ke binciken batun Rasha a cikin zaben, alaƙar da ke tsakanin masu ba da shawara ga Trump da Rasha, da kuma yiwuwar hana shugaban zartar da hukunci.
Ko Trump zai kori mataimakin babban lauya ko kuma a'a, kuma hakan zai kawo gabarar Mr. Mueller, ya zama batun tattaunawa a Washington na tsawon watanni.
A farkon wannan watan, jaridar New York Times ta ruwaito cewa Rosenstein ya yi magana game da amfani da na'urar sauraren sauti don yin rikodin tattaunawar da Trump da kuma yiwuwar maye gurbin shugaban kasa bisa ga Kwaskwarima ta 25.
Rosenstein ya ƙaryata game da wannan jita-jita.
Amma a ranar Litinin da ta gabata, ya shiga fadar White House, a yayin da ake ta rade-radin cewa zai yi murabus.
A maimakon haka, an yi alkawarin ganawa da Trump a ranar Alhamis, wanda a lokacin yake a Majalisar Dinkin Duniya a New York.
Trump ya ce ba zai so ya kori Rosenstein ba, amma sai aka dage taron don kauce wa rikici da sauraron sauraren kwamitin shari'a na majalisar dattawa wanda Kavanaugh da daya daga cikin matan da suka tuhume shi da cin zarafin mata, Dr. Christine Blasey Ford.
A ranar Juma'a ne Trump ya umarci FBI da ta gudanar da bincike na mako guda kan tuhumar da ake yi wa Kavanaugh, wanda hakan ya kara dage kudirin majalisar dattawa.
Mataimakin Trump, Sarah Sanders, ta bayyana a ranar Lahadi a Fox News Channel.
Da aka tambaye ta game da ganawa da Rosenstein, sai ta ce: "An dai ba da ranar da za a yi hakan ba tukuna, amma za a iya yin hakan a wannan makon, kuma za a iya daukan tsawon mako guda saboda duk wani abu da ke faruwa a kotun koli.
Amma za mu gani, kuma ina son a rika sanar da 'yan jarida.
Wasu 'yan jarida za su yi jayayya cewa Sanders ba ta yi wa 'yan jarida jawabi a fadar White House ba tun daga ranar 10 ga Satumba.
Mai watsa shiri Chris Wallace ya tambaye shi dalilin da ya sa.
Sanders ta amsa cewa rage yawan gajeren jawabai ba sakamakon rashin jin daɗin "halayyar wasan kwaikwayo" na 'yan jarida na TV ba, ko da yake ta ce: "Zan yarda da gaskiyar cewa suna yin ƙari".
Bayan haka, ta ce za a ƙara samun hulɗa kai tsaye tsakanin Trump da 'yan jarida.
"Shugaban kasa yana gudanar da taro da amsoshi fiye da duk wani shugaban da ya taba yi", in ji ta ba tare da ta bada wata hujja ba: "Mun ga wadannan lambobin".
Sanders ta ce za a ci gaba da yin gajeren jawabai, amma idan 'yan jarida suka sami damar yin tambaya kai tsaye ga shugaban Amurka, hakan ya fi kyau fiye da yin magana da ni.
Muna kokarin yin hakan sosai, kuma kun ga muna yin hakan a cikin 'yan makonnin nan, kuma waɗannan tattaunawar da shugaban Amurka zai yi za su sauya gajerun jawabai ga manema labarai".
