"Habibullaevic Saipov mai laifi ya yi wa dangin Diego Enrique Angelini, Nicholas Cleves, Ann-Laure Decadt, Darren Drake, Ariel Erle, Hernán Ferrucci, Hernán Diego Mendoza da Alejandro Damián Pagnucca rauni da lahani da hasara, "in ji bukatar da aka gabatar.
